oximated functions for non-convex parts and then develop a simple yet\nefficient iterative algorithm for its solutions. Next, we attempt to maximize\nthe total throughput subject to the number of served IoT devices. Finally,\nnumerical results show that the proposed algorithms significantly outperform\nbenchmark approaches in terms of the number of served IoT devices and system\nthroughput.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2020 08:51:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 07:02:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 17:07:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
