usion can substantially improve the\nquality of reconstructions relative to traditional methods, while also being\npractical to implement and train.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2020 02:32:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 19:20:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 20 Feb 2021 01:06:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-23"}
